Package: mPower
Type: Package
Title: Real Data-based Power Analysis Tool for Microbiome Study Design
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lu Yang and Jun Chen
Maintainer: Lu Yang <luyang1005@gmail.com>
Description: A comprehensive tool designed for power analysis in microbiome study designs. It leverages real data to provide accurate power estimates, aiding researchers in optimizing experimental designs and improving the reliability of their microbiome studies.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
